OL,6,FThe Confederation of British Industry
OL,7,F(CBI), the scandal-hit business lobby
OL,8,Fgroup, said its members had
OL,9,Foverwhelmingly backed reforms aimed
OL,10,Fat restoring the CBI's reputation
